headline: Jacobs to Enhance Regional Transportation in New York State
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected to provide comprehensive design services for the New York State Department of Transportation (NYSDOT) for the lower Hudson Valley region. These services will include bridge replacement, bridge rehabilitation, highway reconstruction and highway rehabilitation projects aimed at improving safety and connectivity north of New York City.
